# Lemonade New Era for Insurance Companies and Quickly Claim Payments (/.Title)

## Overview and Origen (./Overview_and_Origin)
Lemonade Inc. is an insurance company founded by Daniel Schreiber and Shai Wininger and incorporated in April 2015. Back in 2015 Daniel Schreiber had the idea for a technologycal change in insurance Companies since everyboddy needs insurance; then, Shai Wininger came around the idea and signed as cofounder of Lemonade Inc. 



